content: Starting a topic for collaborating on JS guest runtime and bindings

Calvin will be organizing an off-shoot meeting from the interpreted languages group that focuses on JavaScript.
If that's something you're interested in, please message here or DM Calvin directly.
The main goal for the meeting will be to talk about different current approaches in JS guest tooling and how to bring them into the Bytecode Alliance upstream Componentize-JS.
I would also be interested in attending.
